## Limitations

The report is based on available literature and online resources, which may not cover the latest research developments in climate science. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that some interactions and feedbacks are still not fully understood, and ongoing research may provide new insights. The report focuses on general mechanisms and does not delve into region-specific climate impacts or mitigation strategies.